                            <h3>Structural Comparison</h3>
                            <div class="card">
                                <h4>Whaikōrero Structure</h4>
                                <ol>
                                    <li><span class="maori-term">Tauparapara</span> - Opening incantation</li>
                                    <li><span class="maori-term">Whakapapa</span> - Genealogical connections</li>
                                    <li>Reference to the occasion/purpose</li>
                                    <li>Main message/argument</li>
                                    <li>References to landmarks and ancestors</li>
                                    <li>Closing remarks and connection to future</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="card">
                                <h4>Contemporary Debate Structure</h4>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>Introduction and thesis statement</li>
                                    <li>Point 1 with evidence</li>
                                    <li>Point 2 with evidence</li>
                                    <li>Point 3 with evidence</li>
                                    <li>Rebuttal of opposing arguments</li>
                                    <li>Conclusion and call to action</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="activity">
